'''Cali''' '''[[Cali binu Abi Dalib]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: Alī ibn Abī Tālib; [[carabi]]: ﻋﻠﻲ ﺑﻦ ﺃﺑﻲ ﻃﺎﻟﺐ; magaca dhamaystiran Cali ibn Abi Daalib "ﻋﻠﻲ ﺑﻦ ﺃﺑﻲ ﻃﺎﻟﺐ") dhashay [[sanad|13kii Rajab 22 H.K]] Sebtembar 20, 601 [[Kacbada]], [[Makka]] ee dhulka Carabta, isla markaana dhintey [[Bil|21kii Ramadaān 40 H.K]] ≈ Janaayo 27, 661 [[C.D]] [[Masjid|Masjid Kufa]], Kufa, [[Ciraaq]], wuxuu ahaa [[ina adeer]]ka iyo wiilka [[sodog]]a u yahay [[Nebi Muxamed]], hogaamiyihii shanaad ee [[Islam|Dawladda Islaamka]], asxaabi ka mid ah [[Khaliif|Kulafo Raashidiinta]] iyo mid ka mid ah asxaabta rasuulka.<ref>"'''[[Cali bin Dalib]]'''"</ref><ref>"[[ingiriis]]: "Alī ibn Abī Tālib; [[carabi]]: ﻋﻠﻲ ﺑﻦ ﺃﺑﻲ ﻃﺎﻟﺐ; magaca dhamaystiran Cali ibn Abi Daalib "ﻋﻠﻲ ﺑﻦ ﺃﺑﻲ ﻃﺎﻟﺐ""</ref>'''<ref name=i4u>[http://www.islam4theworld.net/sahabah/abu_bakr_r.htm], from [[islam4theworld]]</ref> 

Cali binu abi Daalib wuxuu ka [[wiil]]kii ugu da'da yaraa ee aqbala diinta [[Islaam]]ka kaasi oo dadka raacsan [[Sunni]]gu u yaqaanaan [[Khaliif|Khaliifkii Afaraad]] ee [[Khulafo al-Raashidiinta]]; sidoo kale dadka raacsan [[Shiicada]] waxay u aqoonsan yihiin [[Imaam]]kii kowaad iyo kan xaqa u leh ee ku xiga [[Nebi Muxamed]]. 
Cali wuxuu ahaa hogaamiye ka mid ah [[Khaliif|khulafo al-Raashidiinta]] kaasi oo talada iyo hogaanka maamulka [[Islaam|Dawladda Islaamka]] la wareegay nin yar, ka dib markii uu [[Cusmaan bin Caffan]] dhintey.<ref>"hogaamiye sare ee maamulka [[Islaam|Dawladda Islaamka]]"</ref><ref name="brit">[http://www.britannica.com/EBchecked/topic/2153/Abu-Bakr], from [[Encyclopædia Britannica]]</ref> 

